Brief Introduction About Myself
My name is Elizabeth Nyamarere.I am 20 years old,a student at ALX Africa and also Uzima university studying data science.
I’m currently learning how to use digital tools like Git and GitHub to build my skills.
I am passionate about tech and aspire to help the world soar to greater heights with my tech skills.
I also aspire to help women know more about tech courses and how they can use them to better their lives.
My hobbies are drawing,reading,caligraphy and singing.I enjoy problem-solving and finding better ways to get things done.
Outside of learning,I like connecting with people, trying out new ideas, and improving what I already know. 
I’m excited to build my skills step by step and work on more projects as I gain confidence.
